{"tid":2266421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登競選巴士　遭特朗普支持者車隊包圍","createTime":"2020-11-01T10:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T10:05:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c577e4598c17e895359423267825decc580e035a","tid":2266421,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨總統參選人拜登陣營一輛競選巴士，上周五（10月30日）在德州的高速公路上，被多達100輛總統特朗普支持者的車隊前後包圍，其車身掛有美國國旗和「讓美國再次偉大」（MAGA）的旗幟。拜登陣營其後宣布因安全理由，取消當日在該州奧斯汀北部的造勢活動，民主黨人譴責事件為「危險的騷擾」。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段顯示，插滿支持特朗普旗幟的車隊，於當日一早已在聖安東尼奧和奧斯汀之間的35號洲際公路邊等候，以埋伏拜登陣營的競選大巴。當一輛寫有「拜登-賀錦麗」白色大字的大巴出現時，該車隊便快速跟上並將其包圍；其中一輛黑色輕便客貨車為了追趕大巴甚至切線，結果撞到旁邊的白色汽車。德州特拉維斯縣民主黨女主席納蘭霍（Katie Naranjo）表示，特朗普支持者當時曾向大巴惡言相向。<br />\n<br />\n涉事競選大巴隸屬德州民主黨人，原本計劃用於鼓勵民眾投票，民主黨籍的州眾議員安奇亞（Rafael Anchia）痛批車隊是「特朗普的武裝巨魔」，擾攘競選大巴和交通長達40分鐘。總統特朗普上周六（10月31日）則在Twitter轉發相關片段，並寫道：「我愛德州！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20201101/bkn-20201101170545825-1101_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20201101%2Fbkn-20201101170545825-1101_00972_001.html&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=14a4c089\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20201101/bkn-20201101170545825-1101_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"46d756baf3dc6dc72797be588fc8d641c6dc1b51","tid":2266421,"uid":60563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"你班左膠郁手打侵粉仲惡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff08a2cafbe8752abaa963fe0b313df9c68453c3","tid":2266421,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2B30zHE7DJ0&amp;ab_channel=NowThisNews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2B30zHE7DJ0%26ab_channel%3DNowThisNews&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=f1e44777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2B30zHE7DJ0&amp;ab_channel=NowThisNews</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2c7f6fb4cf582ce9c62705ebf8c94fdea5c37f","tid":2266421,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"早排antifa打trump supporter就睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}